ockquote><br />\n犯法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a1dcd5ab5e82814f346de22f0743cd3fbb3032","tid":149353,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:08:03.000Z","msg":"call的來會率高d"},{"pid":"8c9a9fcc8224318570ac3f4153c668e048027738","tid":149353,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真，如果唔熟路，一個唔覺意兜遠左，乘客會鬧佢有意兜路，不如直接拒絕你好過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家D 導航設備咁方便先進，你班DC9 拎部電話打Candy Crush就識，<br />\n用個Google map 導航就唔識？<br />\n<br />\nbtw~農曆年果時因為帶住小朋友拜年，所以搭左幾次uber。<br />\n由跑馬地去何文田，入隧道果度塞左個幾鐘，<br />\n個司機都冇面黑，如果搭的士既話俾司機屌柒左好耐，仲要全個車程屌屌聲了。<br />\n<br />\n另一次下午三點幾，因為落毛毛雨，所以諗住搭的士，<br />\n點知架架的士都話交更唔載，最終都係uber解決。"},{"pid":"a4f89b0251e54693ca1ffbe83644dd1ec44b92c4","tid":149353,"uid":56060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真，如果唔熟路，一個唔覺意兜遠左，乘客會鬧佢有意兜路，不如直接拒絕你好過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問一句唔熟路可唔可以幫手帶路，再唔係講下會行邊條路有無問題就得啦，選客黎做都咁多藉口"},{"pid":"4902f20a2a34f3fef11db3cff1532afaca230431","tid":149353,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"食緊煙 搵過第二架啦 <br />\n試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48b4090cd1349fbf228af1f6cb23d301d483f1b","tid":149353,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/0Cf1cAXcQrY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0Cf1cAXcQrY&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0e9e8ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0Cf1cAXcQrY</a></blockquote><br />\n條女好撚正"},{"pid":"4b21035080218e97008dec42b6ba85e091dfcbd5","tid":149353,"uid":65320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9的士佬<br />\n上次奉撚住一大箱野<br />\n北角過沙田<br />\n上到車話唔過沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow